00:00:00,010 --> 00:00:33,930
Watch on kissasia.li

1
00:00:36,060 --> 00:00:38,680
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,680 --> 00:00:41,310
=Episode 35=

3
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:44,625
Then what exactly is

4
00:00:44,625 --> 00:00:45,458
the jade token used to command you?

5
00:00:46,375 --> 00:00:47,541
Just a jade token. What else?

6
00:00:48,208 --> 00:00:50,750
No one below a prince or high noble

7
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:52,000
could ever possess one.

8
00:00:53,833 --> 00:00:55,208
It is priceless.

9
00:00:58,166 --> 00:00:59,166
I see.

10
00:01:01,375 --> 00:01:02,875
Someone central to the case,

11
00:01:03,458 --> 00:01:04,750
and someone with the power
to command you.

12
00:01:08,708 --> 00:01:10,250
That leaves only two princes.

13
00:01:10,250 --> 00:01:11,666
Prince Fu and the Crown Prince.

14
00:01:14,041 --> 00:01:14,958
You ask

15
00:01:15,333 --> 00:01:16,291
too many questions.

16
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,291
Did you kill Guan Yunfeng?

17
00:01:20,541 --> 00:01:20,958
Right!

18
00:01:22,083 --> 00:01:23,958
Guan Yunfeng.

19
00:01:26,541 --> 00:01:28,666
He should not have found out my secret.

20
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:11,166
He should not have found out
I knew martial arts.

21
00:02:11,541 --> 00:02:12,041
So,

22
00:02:12,708 --> 00:02:13,958
I had to kill him.

23
00:02:14,833 --> 00:02:15,708
Do you understand now?

24
00:02:16,041 --> 00:02:17,041
Do you understand?

25
00:02:20,875 --> 00:02:22,333
Guan Yunfeng was protecting you.

26
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:23,958
How could you do it?

27
00:02:27,625 --> 00:02:28,708
Protecting me?

28
00:02:29,333 --> 00:02:31,291
Leng Xin needed him to save?

29
00:02:34,416 --> 00:02:36,583
That is hilarious!

30
00:02:40,333 --> 00:02:42,791
Guan Yunfeng was a real man.

31
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:44,791
He deserved better.

32
00:02:45,375 --> 00:02:46,833
He deserved so much better!

33
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,333
I was such a fool.

34
00:02:57,750 --> 00:02:59,708
Before he died, Guan said it.

35
00:03:00,833 --> 00:03:01,541
Taozi.

36
00:03:02,125 --> 00:03:02,708
Leng Xin.

37
00:03:03,958 --> 00:03:05,416
Why didn't I see it?

38
00:03:09,166 --> 00:03:09,833
Leng Xin.

39
00:03:11,333 --> 00:03:12,583
You monster.

40
00:03:13,250 --> 00:03:14,750
You will die horribly!

41
00:03:15,208 --> 00:03:17,000
I'm sure I will!

42
00:03:17,166 --> 00:03:18,250
But you won't live to see it!

43
00:03:18,958 --> 00:03:19,541
Fine.

44
00:03:20,416 --> 00:03:21,500
Then kill me.

45
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,500
Use your cruelest method.

46
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:29,083
The one you are best at!

47
00:03:32,625 --> 00:03:33,500
Don't worry.

48
00:03:35,083 --> 00:03:37,000
You are Xintian's dear sister.

49
00:03:38,250 --> 00:03:40,416
I won't make it hurt too much.

50
00:03:42,833 --> 00:03:43,458
Die!

51
00:04:17,890 --> 00:04:22,600
♪In a fleeting moment♪

52
00:04:24,300 --> 00:04:28,600
♪Whose face crosses my mind♪

53
00:04:30,850 --> 00:04:35,640
♪Whose name is it♪

54
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:41,010
♪I whisper in my heart♪

55
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:47,980
♪Yet in the crowd, we brush past♪

56
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:51,930
♪Only then did I understand fate♪

57
00:04:51,930 --> 00:04:55,600
♪Was hidden in the day we met♪

58
00:04:56,470 --> 00:04:59,970
♪A fate that cannot be severed♪

59
00:05:00,970 --> 00:05:03,300
♪Round and round♪

60
00:05:03,510 --> 00:05:07,760
♪Threads of love bind us together♪

61
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:12,390
♪Afraid love will fade like smoke♪

62
00:05:14,010 --> 00:05:20,220
♪Afraid memories will fade like dreams♪

63
00:05:20,350 --> 00:05:23,970
♪This longing I cannot say♪

64
00:05:24,180 --> 00:05:29,140
♪I wish you could hear♪

65
00:05:53,850 --> 00:05:58,220
♪Afraid love will fade like smoke♪

66
00:06:00,010 --> 00:06:06,680
♪Afraid memories will fade like dreams♪

67
00:06:06,970 --> 00:06:10,220
♪This longing I cannot say♪

68
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:15,720
♪Tucked away inside my heart♪

69
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:35,666
I killed her.

70
00:06:38,666 --> 00:06:39,333
I killed her.

71
00:06:59,875 --> 00:07:01,250
Good! Another one dead.

72
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:05,000
Go join Guan Yunfeng.

73
00:07:08,083 --> 00:07:09,458
Xintian! Xintian!

74
00:07:10,083 --> 00:07:10,666
Xintian!

75
00:07:11,291 --> 00:07:12,000
Xintian!

76
00:07:15,916 --> 00:07:16,916
She is dead.

77
00:07:17,375 --> 00:07:18,708
Nothing stands between us now.

78
00:07:24,541 --> 00:07:26,250
Will you run away with me?

79
00:07:28,333 --> 00:07:29,750
Run away with you?

80
00:07:33,166 --> 00:07:34,875
After all the people you killed?

81
00:07:37,166 --> 00:07:38,083
In your dreams!

82
00:07:40,500 --> 00:07:41,291
Xintian.

83
00:07:42,791 --> 00:07:43,833
I killed because

84
00:07:43,833 --> 00:07:45,833
I was raised to be a killer.

85
00:07:46,333 --> 00:07:47,416
Killing is all I know.

86
00:07:47,833 --> 00:07:49,791
If I didn't kill, I couldn't survive.

87
00:07:50,291 --> 00:07:51,833
But I don't like killing.

88
00:07:54,208 --> 00:07:54,666
Xintian.

89
00:07:55,625 --> 00:07:57,041
You are the only one
who was ever kind to me.

90
00:07:57,583 --> 00:07:58,708
I truly care about you.

91
00:07:59,250 --> 00:07:59,916
Let's go.

92
00:08:00,125 --> 00:08:01,833
Let's leave this all behind.

93
00:08:02,041 --> 00:08:03,583
I will care for you like my own sister.

94
00:08:05,625 --> 00:08:07,916
Please, Xintian. Come with me.

95
00:08:09,833 --> 00:08:10,625
Taozi.

96
00:08:12,083 --> 00:08:13,083
Just looking at you now

97
00:08:13,833 --> 00:08:15,333
makes me sick.

98
00:08:16,916 --> 00:08:17,916
I regret it.

99
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,291
I regret being kind to you.

100
00:08:21,625 --> 00:08:23,000
I regret taking you in.

101
00:08:25,750 --> 00:08:26,500
Someone like you...

102
00:08:27,458 --> 00:08:28,666
After killing so many people,

103
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:31,000
you deserve to be cut to pieces.

104
00:08:31,083 --> 00:08:32,500
You should rot in hell!

105
00:08:36,125 --> 00:08:37,291
I was so good to you.

106
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:39,958
Why would you curse me?

107
00:08:40,916 --> 00:08:41,750
Curse you?

108
00:08:42,916 --> 00:08:44,000
I want to do more than curse you.

109
00:08:44,208 --> 00:08:45,791
I want to kill you!

110
00:08:45,958 --> 00:08:47,958
I will kill you with my own hands!

111
00:08:56,416 --> 00:08:57,000
Fake.

112
00:08:58,416 --> 00:08:59,291
It was all fake.

113
00:09:01,375 --> 00:09:02,375
Everything you did for me

114
00:09:02,541 --> 00:09:03,541
was fake!

115
00:09:08,250 --> 00:09:08,791
Yes.

116
00:09:09,583 --> 00:09:10,791
It was fake.

117
00:09:12,125 --> 00:09:13,375
Did you really think

118
00:09:14,166 --> 00:09:15,583
someone as evil as you

119
00:09:16,250 --> 00:09:17,166
deserved kindness?

120
00:09:18,666 --> 00:09:19,916
No one will ever love you.

121
00:09:20,750 --> 00:09:23,333
You are just a pathetic thing
nobody cares!

122
00:09:25,458 --> 00:09:27,000
I will ask you one last time.

123
00:09:29,166 --> 00:09:30,166
Are you coming with me?

124
00:09:31,791 --> 00:09:32,708
Are you coming?

125
00:09:36,416 --> 00:09:37,666
Tell me!

126
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,791
Never.

127
00:09:51,666 --> 00:09:52,333
Fine.

128
00:09:53,416 --> 00:09:54,458
Then die.

129
00:09:56,041 --> 00:09:56,916
Go join the dead.

130
00:09:57,708 --> 00:09:58,708
I'll send you there.

131
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:01,958
I'll kill you!

132
00:10:08,125 --> 00:10:08,958
Wait.

133
00:10:20,583 --> 00:10:21,333
You are scared.

134
00:10:22,958 --> 00:10:23,916
Beg me.

135
00:10:29,041 --> 00:10:29,625
Taozi.

136
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:33,541
No.

137
00:10:34,333 --> 00:10:35,000
Leng Xin.

138
00:10:36,375 --> 00:10:37,875
I could never be afraid of you.

139
00:10:47,875 --> 00:10:48,750
Listen to me.

140
00:10:49,500 --> 00:10:50,750
Untie me if you have the nerve.

141
00:10:51,416 --> 00:10:52,416
Fight me.

142
00:10:56,458 --> 00:10:57,416
Fight you?

143
00:11:01,041 --> 00:11:01,916
You?

144
00:11:03,083 --> 00:11:04,458
You want to fight me?

145
00:11:07,666 --> 00:11:08,291
Xintian.

146
00:11:08,833 --> 00:11:09,791
You are adorable.

147
00:11:12,083 --> 00:11:14,000
What is wrong? Are you scared?

148
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,000
You don't dare, do you?

149
00:11:18,083 --> 00:11:19,041
You don't dare.

150
00:11:19,041 --> 00:11:19,625
Fine!

151
00:11:21,708 --> 00:11:22,750
You are my dear sister.

152
00:11:23,583 --> 00:11:24,750
I will listen to you.

153
00:11:27,541 --> 00:11:28,500
I will untie you.

154
00:11:29,125 --> 00:11:30,208
Let's fight.

155
00:11:50,083 --> 00:11:50,708
Hurry up.

156
00:12:03,458 --> 00:12:03,875
Come on.

157
00:12:08,666 --> 00:12:09,458
You are older than me.

158
00:12:10,291 --> 00:12:11,416
I will give you three moves.

159
00:12:14,333 --> 00:12:15,000
Leng Xin.

160
00:12:16,833 --> 00:12:18,500
I will kill you myself.

161
00:12:23,916 --> 00:12:24,708
Take him!

162
00:12:27,416 --> 00:12:29,708
Who did you say you were?

163
00:12:30,666 --> 00:12:31,583
Mr. Duan, I'm...

164
00:12:33,083 --> 00:12:34,333
You are an assassin.

165
00:12:34,333 --> 00:12:34,916
I'm not!

166
00:12:35,250 --> 00:12:37,083
Take him somewhere no one can see.

167
00:12:39,666 --> 00:12:40,166
Yes!

168
00:12:41,666 --> 00:12:42,000
Move!

169
00:12:42,125 --> 00:12:42,791
Let go of me!

170
00:12:43,083 --> 00:12:43,583
Stop!

171
00:12:46,583 --> 00:12:47,000
Mr. Lu.

172
00:12:51,125 --> 00:12:52,000
Lu.

173
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,375
What was that you shouted?

174
00:12:54,791 --> 00:12:55,875
His name is Xu Duoyu.

175
00:12:56,500 --> 00:12:57,750
He is a registered Squad Leader

176
00:12:58,166 --> 00:12:59,791
of our Northern Bureau.

177
00:13:00,333 --> 00:13:01,083
He is no assassin.

178
00:13:01,541 --> 00:13:02,416
Even a Jinyiwei

179
00:13:03,166 --> 00:13:05,041
cannot force his way
into the imperial city.

180
00:13:05,083 --> 00:13:05,958
I have urgent confidential business.

181
00:13:06,250 --> 00:13:08,125
I must see Young Duke Chang Beiming.

182
00:13:09,250 --> 00:13:10,125
Confidential business?

183
00:13:10,458 --> 00:13:12,250
That sounds reasonable enough.

184
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,750
Entering the imperial city

185
00:13:15,041 --> 00:13:16,708
without an edict or golden token

186
00:13:16,875 --> 00:13:18,250
is treason.

187
00:13:18,750 --> 00:13:20,500
I could execute him on the spot,

188
00:13:20,791 --> 00:13:21,916
and no one could fault me.

189
00:13:23,291 --> 00:13:23,916
Mr. Duan.

190
00:13:24,458 --> 00:13:26,125
He is with our Northern Bureau.

191
00:13:26,333 --> 00:13:27,250
Lu Guokai.

192
00:13:28,416 --> 00:13:30,041
What rank are you?

193
00:13:30,625 --> 00:13:32,875
You dare bargain with me here?

194
00:13:33,125 --> 00:13:34,250
You are not qualified.

195
00:13:34,458 --> 00:13:35,166
Then am I

196
00:13:35,750 --> 00:13:37,375
qualified enough?

197
00:13:37,375 --> 00:13:37,791
Mr. Zhang.

198
00:13:37,791 --> 00:13:38,375
Mr. Zhang.

199
00:13:38,375 --> 00:13:38,791
Mr. Zhang.

200
00:13:43,958 --> 00:13:44,750
Are you all right?

201
00:13:45,916 --> 00:13:47,583
Mr. Zhang, if I don't get inside,

202
00:13:48,166 --> 00:13:49,958
disaster may fall
on the Northern Bureau.

203
00:13:52,583 --> 00:13:53,125
Guokai.

204
00:13:54,250 --> 00:13:55,166
Return to the Bureau at once.

205
00:13:55,791 --> 00:13:56,125
Yes.

206
00:13:56,750 --> 00:13:57,333
Zuo Da. Jiang Biao.

207
00:13:57,541 --> 00:13:57,916
Yes.

208
00:13:57,958 --> 00:13:58,666
Stay and guard the imperial city.

209
00:13:59,000 --> 00:13:59,375
Yes.

210
00:13:59,458 --> 00:13:59,875
The rest of you,

211
00:14:00,291 --> 00:14:00,791
come with me.

212
00:14:01,250 --> 00:14:01,666
Yes.

213
00:14:09,750 --> 00:14:11,625
Zhang Weimin, why are you everywhere?

214
00:14:12,291 --> 00:14:14,750
This is not your
Northern Bureau's post. How dare you!

215
00:14:20,250 --> 00:14:22,666
Zhang Weimin, you dare hit me?

216
00:14:31,458 --> 00:14:32,916
Mr. Duan, are you all right?

217
00:14:39,291 --> 00:14:39,666
You...

218
00:14:53,125 --> 00:14:53,916
I told you.

219
00:14:54,875 --> 00:14:55,916
You cannot beat me.

220
00:15:01,458 --> 00:15:02,041
Leng Xin.

221
00:15:02,833 --> 00:15:04,125
Today, either you die

222
00:15:04,583 --> 00:15:05,750
or I do.

223
00:15:13,958 --> 00:15:14,625
You are mad!

224
00:15:15,041 --> 00:15:16,500
You think I won't kill you?

225
00:15:17,750 --> 00:15:18,333
Leng Xin.

226
00:15:19,166 --> 00:15:20,708
You are a coward!

227
00:15:22,375 --> 00:15:23,000
What did you say?

228
00:15:23,916 --> 00:15:25,708
I said you are a coward.

229
00:15:26,291 --> 00:15:27,625
You want people to be kind to you,

230
00:15:28,125 --> 00:15:29,791
but you are terrified when they are.

231
00:15:30,333 --> 00:15:32,000
You want to be loved,

232
00:15:32,541 --> 00:15:34,166
yet you are afraid of it.

233
00:15:35,250 --> 00:15:37,000
You fear your master.

234
00:15:37,541 --> 00:15:39,416
You are nothing but his weapon!

235
00:15:39,708 --> 00:15:40,375
How pathetic!

236
00:15:40,916 --> 00:15:41,625
Shut up.

237
00:15:42,375 --> 00:15:43,125
I will kill you.

238
00:15:47,708 --> 00:15:48,625
I will kill you!

239
00:15:53,750 --> 00:15:54,250
(Young Duke.)

240
00:15:54,708 --> 00:15:55,500
(Taozi is Leng Xin.)

241
00:15:55,791 --> 00:15:56,708
(Bingfan and Xintian are in danger.)

242
00:15:59,125 --> 00:16:00,666
How are you alive?

243
00:16:01,875 --> 00:16:03,041
Without this little act,

244
00:16:03,958 --> 00:16:05,208
how could we make you tell the truth?

245
00:16:06,458 --> 00:16:07,208
An act?

246
00:16:07,583 --> 00:16:09,125
I knew it

247
00:16:09,708 --> 00:16:10,666
as soon as Bingfan started.

248
00:16:11,500 --> 00:16:12,750
Everything just now

249
00:16:13,375 --> 00:16:14,541
was meant to provoke you.

250
00:16:15,916 --> 00:16:16,833
(Then kill me.)

251
00:16:17,666 --> 00:16:19,125
(Use your cruelest method.)

252
00:16:19,416 --> 00:16:20,708
(The one you are best at!)

253
00:16:28,041 --> 00:16:28,875
Understand now?

254
00:16:31,041 --> 00:16:31,625
I don't believe it.

255
00:16:32,500 --> 00:16:33,625
I checked.

256
00:16:33,875 --> 00:16:35,125
She had no pulse!

257
00:16:35,916 --> 00:16:37,041
There was blood at her mouth.

258
00:16:38,083 --> 00:16:38,666
Taozi.

259
00:16:39,750 --> 00:16:40,208
No.

260
00:16:41,166 --> 00:16:41,875
Leng Xin.

261
00:16:42,375 --> 00:16:43,708
You are far too sure of yourself.

262
00:16:45,375 --> 00:16:47,708
I knew Leng Xin likes to kill
with one thrust to the heart.

263
00:16:48,500 --> 00:16:49,041
So,

264
00:16:49,750 --> 00:16:50,750
thank you for the fruit.

265
00:16:52,125 --> 00:16:53,666
I put an orange under my arm.

266
00:16:54,625 --> 00:16:55,958
When you checked my pulse,

267
00:16:56,291 --> 00:16:57,666
I squeezed it tight

268
00:16:57,916 --> 00:16:58,875
and cut off the blood flow.

269
00:16:59,291 --> 00:17:00,625
So you felt nothing.

270
00:17:01,958 --> 00:17:03,583
As for the heart you stabbed,

271
00:17:03,875 --> 00:17:04,958
and why it felt no different,

272
00:17:05,750 --> 00:17:07,666
Duoyu knew you might try that.

273
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:09,125
So he made

274
00:17:09,125 --> 00:17:10,583
a soft armor called Trueheart.

275
00:17:10,958 --> 00:17:11,708
It has blood pouches inside.

276
00:17:11,916 --> 00:17:13,000
When pierced,

277
00:17:13,083 --> 00:17:15,083
it feels exactly like the real thing.

278
00:17:15,791 --> 00:17:17,000
It even bleeds.

279
00:17:18,291 --> 00:17:19,250
The blood at my mouth?

280
00:17:20,083 --> 00:17:20,791
I bit myself.

281
00:17:27,333 --> 00:17:27,750
You...

282
00:17:28,416 --> 00:17:29,333
You tricked me!

283
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:30,500
Leng Xin.

284
00:17:31,291 --> 00:17:32,458
Today is the Ghost Festival.

285
00:17:32,916 --> 00:17:34,000
It will also be your death day.

286
00:17:40,708 --> 00:17:41,041
Don't run!

287
00:18:02,916 --> 00:18:04,125
You sneaky wildcat.

288
00:18:15,125 --> 00:18:15,958
Don't let her escape.

289
00:18:16,041 --> 00:18:16,375
Get her!

290
00:18:25,333 --> 00:18:25,958
Take men and put out the fire.

291
00:18:26,041 --> 00:18:26,333
Yes!

292
00:18:26,333 --> 00:18:27,041
The rest, follow me!

293
00:18:27,208 --> 00:18:27,625
Yes!

294
00:18:31,791 --> 00:18:32,166
Put out the fire!

295
00:18:32,375 --> 00:18:32,791
Put it out!

296
00:18:45,930 --> 00:18:49,100
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

297
00:18:49,470 --> 00:18:52,850
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

298
00:18:53,100 --> 00:18:56,100
♪My heart drifted lost♪

299
00:18:56,100 --> 00:18:59,510
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

300
00:19:00,600 --> 00:19:03,810
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

301
00:19:04,220 --> 00:19:07,560
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

302
00:19:08,140 --> 00:19:10,350
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

303
00:19:10,350 --> 00:19:14,390
♪I've softly let it go♪

304
00:19:14,390 --> 00:19:18,260
♪The vow you made was true♪

305
00:19:18,260 --> 00:19:22,010
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

306
00:19:22,310 --> 00:19:24,220
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

307
00:19:24,220 --> 00:19:28,760
♪And forget at world's end♪

308
00:19:29,060 --> 00:19:30,560
♪Embracing memory♪

309
00:19:30,560 --> 00:19:32,930
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

310
00:19:32,930 --> 00:19:36,810
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

311
00:19:36,810 --> 00:19:39,140
♪I wish to let it pass♪

312
00:19:39,140 --> 00:19:44,140
♪And run toward this vast life♪

